  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育系统的架构图，核心是成绩同步服务GradeSync，它要连接多个数据源和内容分发节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，GradeSync作为中心节点。那它连接的数据源具体有哪些？我看到有学生数据库和内容CDN两类？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，学生数据库需要三个实例——分别对应本科生、研究生和继续教育的数据。另外内容CDN也需要两个节点，一个国内一个海外。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出GradeSync中心节点，然后往右边展开三个StudentDB实例和两个ContentCDN节点，全部用实线连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "结构是对的，但三个StudentDB最好标注一下区分，比如B是本科生库，C是研究生库，G是继续教育库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我调整一下标签。刚才G节点的位置放得太远了，我把它收拢到和B、C同一层，保持视觉整齐。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "ContentCDN那两个节点，D和E，D是国内CDN，E是海外CDN，GradeSync会根据学生地区智能路由。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下连接关系：GradeSync到五个下游节点都是直接连接，没有中间层，也没有双向箭头，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，都是GradeSync主动拉取或推送的单向数据流。不过我突然想到，五个下游节点会不会让图太宽？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以用TD布局，GradeSync放顶部，五个节点垂直向下展开，这样宽度可控，层次也清晰。StudentDB三个放左边列，CDN两个放右边列。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "这个布局很好，一目了然。最终就是GradeSync连三个StudentDB、两个ContentCDN，总共五条线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成，已按TD布局绘制，所有节点命名规范，连接关系清晰。可以归档了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
